      "code": "self.self.setLandingLag(true);\nself.self.playAttackSound(1);\nself.effect = self.self.pushEffectBehind(self.self.attachEffect(\"samus_explosion\", { scaleX: 1.15, scaleY: 1.15, x: self.self.flipX(34.5), y: -65.7 }));\nself.effectCo = [self.self.flipX(34.5), -65.7];\nself.self.createTimer(1, 2, self.effectFollow);\nself.effect2 = self.self.attachEffect(\"samus_explosion2\", { scaleX: 1.15, scaleY: 1.15, x: self.self.flipX(34.5), y: -65.7 });\nreturn;",
