      "code": "self.self.updateAttackBoxStats(1, { direction: 75, hitStun: 3, power: 40, kbConstant: 25 });\nself.self.updateAttackBoxStats(2, { direction: 75, hitStun: 3, power: 40, kbConstant: 25 });\nself.self.updateAttackBoxStats(3, { direction: 75, hitStun: 5, power: 50, kbConstant: 25 });\nself.self.refreshAttackID();\nself.self.playAttackSound(1);\nself.effect = self.self.pushEffectBehind(self.self.attachEffect(\"samus_explosion\", { scaleX: 1.07, scaleY: 1.07, x: self.self.flipX(43.2), y: -51.7 }));\nself.effectCo = [self.self.flipX(42.3), -51.7];\nself.self.createTimer(1, 2, self.effectFollow);\nself.effect2 = self.self.attachEffect(\"samus_explosion2\", { scaleX: 1.07, scaleY: 1.07, x: self.self.flipX(43.2), y: -51.7 });\nreturn;",
